item.title: Our goal's job, by @cobyism
item.description:
Our goal's job, by @cobyism

Our goal's job February 19, 2016 Â· 1.185 min read What is a goal actually for? First off, a goal is for getting us moving. Picking a goal, and making a start in that direction-even if it isn't the "right" goal (whatever that means)-at least gets us moving forward.
